condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :1. Project Management Agreement | Description :Project Management Agreement approved and Subsidiary Agreementbetween MoF and SENELEC in place | Due Date :30-Apr-2012
Finance Agreement :2. Project Implementation Manual | Description :Preparation of PIM acceptable to the Association | Due Date:30-Apr-2012
Finance Agreement :3. Financial Management | Description :Appointment of FM Specialist for the project | Due Date :30-Aug-2012
Finance Agreement :4. Financial covenant 1: SENELEC’s revenue adjustment | Description :Refer to Section V.A of FinancingAgreement. Covenant not yet due. | Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :5. Financial covenant 2: Accounts Receivables | Description :Refer to Section V.B of Financing Agreement.Covenant not yet due. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :6. Financial covenant 3: Debt Service Coverage Ratio | Description :Refer to Section V.C of Financing Agreement.Covenant not yet due. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Front-end Fee | Description :The Front-end Fee payable by the Recipient shall be equal to one quarter of onepercent (Â¼ of 1%) of the Credit amount. The Recipient shall pay the Front-end Fee not later than sixty days after the EffectiveDate. Article II, 2.03 of the Financing Agreement. | Due Date :31-Dec-2016

Finance Agreement :Internal auditor | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall, not later than one (1) month after theEffective Date, employ and thereafter maintain at all times during project implementation, an internal auditor whosequalifications, experience and terms of reference shall be acceptable to the Association. Section I, A of the Project Agreement (2)| Due Date :24-Feb-2016

Finance Agreement :Procurement Specialist for PMU | Description :Hiring of dedicated procurement specialist for the projectmanagement unit. Refer to Project Agreement Section I.A. (3) | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Manual | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall, not later than (1) monthafter the Effective Date (a) update under TOR acceptable to the Association & furnish to the Recipient & the Association animplementation manual for the Project containing detailed arrangements & procedures specified in Section I, C, 1 of the ProjectAgreement & thereafter adopt such PIM as shall have been approved by the Association | Due Date :24-Feb-2016
Finance Agreement :Project Management Unit in place | Description :Dedicated project unit in place | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Project accounting software | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall, not later than three (3)months after the Effective Date update its accounting software to include the Project. Section II, B, 3. | Due Date :24-Apr-2017
